('4e931130-3070-48b3-8044-113a4bb83359', 'password_reset_request', 'Password Reset Request', 1, 'generic', '42Viral Password Reset Requested', '<p>\r\n#{Person.first_name},\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe have received a request for resetting your 42Viral account password. Follow the link below to complete the reset operation. The link is valid 24 hours from the time it was generated and will expire after that.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n#{_server_address}users/pass_reset/#{reset_authorization_token}\r\n</p>', 'default', '2011-10-10 10:37:20', '4e27efec-ece0-4a36-baaf-38384bb83359', '2011-10-10 10:37:20', '4e27efec-ece0-4a36-baaf-38384bb83359');